# Auto-request a review from verdacciobot on release ("build: release packages") PRs.
#
# The Changesets version PR always rewrites CHANGELOG.md for every bumped package,
# whereas feature PRs only add files under .changeset/. Owning the changelogs makes
# GitHub request verdacciobot's review on the release PR without firing on every PR.
#
# Note: verdacciobot must be a repo collaborator (read access) for this to take
# effect, and this file must live on the default branch.

CHANGELOG.md      @verdacciobot
**/CHANGELOG.md   @verdacciobot
